# Parse Meeting Log

## Description
Parse and analyze Zoom meeting logs for debugging and troubleshooting.

## Purpose
Extract useful information from meeting logs including participant actions, errors, and system events.

## Usage
```
parse_meeting_log <meeting_log_path>
```

## Features
- Extract participant information
- Timeline of events
- Error detection
- Performance metrics

## Keywords
meeting, log, parse, zoom, debug, participant
